name: Froggi
description: Froggi is an on-chain inscription token on base that generates SVG metadata to inscribe art directly onto the tokens without any IPFS or third party. It is the next evolution of standard Token that can do more, all while staying completely verifiable on-chain without any third party database, image base, cloudflare, or image storage otherwise which is what makes it shine above others.
